// Action — in Defender for Endpoint:
// Device → <HOST> → Isolate device
// Keep MDE comms allowed so forensics can pull artefacts.

// Export the AlertDetail report. Capture:
// - Destination IP/domain, TI verdict, volume, beacon period
// - Source host, process, isolation timestamp
// - Tenant scope summary

// Export the AlertDetail report with:
// - Scan source + ports + allowed destinations
// - Compromised account list
// - AD recon evidence (if any)
// Attach to Tier 2 / IR engagement.

// Action — in Entra admin centre:
// Roles → <ROLE> → Remove assignment for <GRANTEE>
// Confirm AzureActivity ROLEASSIGNMENTS/DELETE event lands.

// Disable both the assigning and the granted account.
// Rotate any Key Vault secrets accessed during the window:
AzureActivity
| where Caller == "<GRANTEE>"
| where OperationNameValue has "KEYVAULT/SECRETS"
| project TimeGenerated, ResourceId, Properties

